snippet.title: I, Robot - Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
I, Robot is launching on April 17th! Overcome everything and rebel against the evil eye by any means necessary. Pre-order I, Robot today! 

Pre-Order and Wishlist: https://urals.co/atari/i-robot
